.br
       512 Ctrl\-Alt\-9 Liu's IM(Boshiamy IM)
.br
      1024 Ctrl\-Alt\-0 Internal encoding IM
.br
      2048 Ctrl\-Alt\-\- Simple Chanjei IM
.br
      4096 Ctrl\-Alt\-= Japanese Kana and Kanji IM
.br
      8192 Ctrl\-Alt\-` Greek letters IM
.br
